Édition de 1899</td>
<td width="33%" style="text-align:right;font-size:90%;"><a href="/wiki/Bible_du_Rabbinat_1899/Amos" title="Bible du Rabbinat 1899/Amos">Amos</a><span class="%5B%5BBible+du+Rabbinat+1899%2FAmos%7CAmos%5D%5DhiddenStructure" style="color:#808080">&#160;&#160;►</span></td>
